label: CIIC 152. Ballinrannig V
sitetype: Burial ground and probable ecclesiastical site
recording: First recognised in 1782 by Pelham and recorded by Vallancey (1804) in 6, 226. This stone was recorded for the Ogham in 3D project in 2017 by Helena Zacharias, a participant on the Corca Dhuibhne 3d project, using Structure from Motion 3d technology.
